{"tid":1432364,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"錢大康向盧偉聰就學生會會長被捕事件提3問題","createTime":"2019-08-08T08:23:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-08T09:58:12.000Z","uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"7a84c977cafee7347b97d17a30d7865fcd8be098","tid":1432364,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T08:23:21.000Z","msg":"浸大學生會評議會主席雷樂希表示，浸大校長錢大康今早向警務處處長盧偉聰提出3條問題，包括為甚麼觀星筆是攻擊性武器、為何未經使用的觀星筆可斷定為武器，以及警方為何可以對方仲賢使用過度武力，錢大康將會在下午5時半發出校內電郵交代事件。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1473450-20190808.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1473450-20190808.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=g7cViP25SqI%2F%2FE6cIGpO76bKco4j3WCMPlNn4btP894%3D&h=27cf3cb4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1473450-20190808.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=65c67f1f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1473450-20190808.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"eea39bc4698d4a6ebd742685d5a055a15a85b416","tid":1432364,"uid":5499,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T08:27:01.000Z","msg":"呢隻錢大康都係快ed番大灣區啦"},{"pid":"9572c2c5160fb37c0c8096ddc694a41be5a96a02","tid":1432364,"uid":4189,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T09:56:37.000Z","msg":"下午5時半?<br />\n5你老母?"},{"pid":"f080e7bfec0e8f191315edee282789d9f5e305f4","tid":1432364,"uid":810,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T09:57:32.000Z","msg":"what time is it now?"},{"pid":"e9f869a60db8074f2fac9f83b5751c79d8aa010f","tid":1432364,"uid":143382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T09:58:12.000Z","msg":"係今朝問警方，下就對外公開"}]}